 been an early sign of her madness referencesedit  lacayo richard  october  the sunshine boy time at the turn of the th century history painting was the highest purpose art could serve and turner would attempt those heights all his life but his real achievement would be to make landscape the equal of history painting   joseph mallord william turner national gallery retrieved  october    a b shanes eric  the life and masterworks of jmw turner th ed new york parkstone press isbn    herrmann luke october  joseph mallord william turner oxford dictionary of national biography oxford university press   a b hamilton james  turner new york random house chapter  isbn  subscription required help   bailey anthony  standing in the sun a life of jmw turner london pimlico p  isbn  subscription required help   a b wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    brown david blayney december  joseph mallord william turner – in brown david blayney jmw turner sketchbooks drawings and watercolours tate research publications isbn  retrieved  march    a b wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    thornbury george walter  the life of jmw turner p    hamilton james   turner  a life london sceptre isbn    thornbury george walter  the life of jmw turner p    finberg a j  the life of jmw turner ra clarendon press p    a b hamilton james  turner new york random house chapter  isbn    wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    cunningham peter  december  obituary of turner the athenaeum pp –   butlin martin joll evelyn  the paintings of jmw turner rev ed new haven yale university press isbn    wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    roberts miquette the unknown turner tate retrieved  july    turner biography  chronology – the tu