ed william turner b  turner is believed to have been born some time between late april and early may  his exact date of birth is unknown the date of  april which is both saint georges day and the supposed birthday of william shakespeare was the date turner himself claimed to have been born but this claim has never been verified the first verifiable date is that turner was baptised on  may this casts some doubt on  april date as high infant mortality rates meant parents would usually baptise their children shortly after birth c mary marshall died in  after having been committed in  to st lukes hospital and then to the bethlem royal hospital a mental asylum her illness possibly due in part to the early death of turners younger sister hamilton suggests that this fit of illness may have been an early sign of her madness referencesedit  lacayo richard  october  the sunshine boy time at the turn of the th century history painting was the highest purpose art could serve and turner would attempt those heights all his life but his real achievement would be to make landscape the equal of history painting   joseph mallord william turner national gallery retrieved  october    a b shanes eric  the life and masterworks of jmw turner th ed new york parkstone press isbn    herrmann luke october  joseph mallord william turner oxford dictionary of national biography oxford university press   a b hamilton james  turner new york random house chapter  isbn  subscription required help   bailey anthony  standing in the sun a life of jmw turner london pimlico p  isbn  subscription required help   a b wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    brown david blayney december  joseph mallord william turner – in brown david blayney jmw turner sketchbooks drawings and watercolours tate research publications isbn  retrieved  march    a b wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  hudson p  isbn    wilton andrew  turner in his time new ed london thames  h